    #   - Install Tailscale (official apt repo) + enable tailscaled
    #   - Download ttyd binary (github.com/tsl0922/ttyd releases, amd64)
    #   - Download wifi-connect binary (balena-io/wifi-connect releases)
    #   - Drop first-boot systemd unit + wrapper (flag check, wifi-connect AP
    #     "HomeNAS-Setup", write /etc/homenas/provisioned on success)
